%% Trace: features/01-編輯Email.feature + 02-編輯手機發送OTP + 03-編輯手機完成更新.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Ctrl as AccountContactController
    participant Auth as JwtAuthGuard
    participant Svc as ContactEditService
    participant OtpSvc as OtpService
    participant SMS as ItSmsGateway
    participant Mail as MailGateway
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant CRM as CrmCustomerGateway

    Note over User,FE: 使用者已登入

    alt 編輯 Email (不需 OTP)
        User->>FE: 帳號設定 → 編輯 Email → 輸入新 Email
        FE->>Ctrl: PUT /account/bindings/email (new_email) [Bearer]
        Ctrl->>Auth: validateJwt
        Ctrl->>Svc: updateEmail(currentUserId, new_email)
        Svc->>Repo: findByEmailHash(newEmailHash) - 唯一性
        Repo-->>Svc: null
        Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET email=new_email
        Svc->>CRM: updateCustomerEmail
        Svc->>Mail: send "Email 變更確認" 至 new_email (CLARIFY-04)
        Svc-->>Ctrl: updated
        Ctrl-->>FE: 200 OK
    else 編輯手機 (兩步)
        User->>FE: 帳號設定 → 編輯手機 → 輸入新手機
        FE->>Ctrl: POST /account/bindings/mobile/edit-send-otp (new_mobile) [Bearer]
        Ctrl->>Svc: prepareEditMobile(currentUserId, new_mobile)
        Svc->>Repo: findByMobileHash - 唯一性
        Repo-->>Svc: null
        Svc->>OtpSvc: issue(contact=new_mobile, purpose=REGISTER, channel=sms)
        OtpSvc->>SMS: enqueue
        OtpSvc-->>Svc: otp_uuid
        Ctrl-->>FE: 200 {otp_uuid}

        User->>FE: 輸入 OTP
        FE->>Ctrl: PUT /account/bindings/mobile (otp_uuid, otp_code)
        Ctrl->>Svc: updateMobile(currentUserId, otp_uuid, otp_code)
        Svc->>OtpSvc: verify
        OtpSvc-->>Svc: ok
        Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET mobile_phone=new_mobile
        Svc->>CRM: updateCustomerMobile
        Svc->>SMS: send "手機變更確認" 至 new_mobile (CLARIFY-04)
        Svc-->>Ctrl: updated
        Ctrl-->>FE: 200 OK
    end
    FE-->>User: 顯示新聯絡方式
